# Custom Base64-like Decoding Utility
function Decode-CustomBase64 {
    param([string]$EncodedString)
    
    # Define the custom charset
    $customCharset = 'Q9x7RnS4yT3kL2mN1pG6jH5fB8dC0vZ' + 
                     'W-wU_aX+qE=uY/K.tM!iO$hP&bD*J'
    $standardBase64Chars = 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789+/='
    
    # Reverse the rotation
    $unrotated = -join($EncodedString[($EncodedString.Length-1)..0])
    
    # Decode using custom charset
    $decoded = $unrotated | ForEach-Object {
        $char = $_
        if ($customCharset.Contains($char)) {
            $index = $customCharset.IndexOf($char)
            $standardBase64Chars[$index]
        } else {
            $char
        }
    }
    
    $standardBase64 = -join $decoded
    return [System.Convert]::FromBase64String($standardBase64)
}

# Advanced Distributed Decryption Function
function Invoke-AdvancedScriptDecryption {
    param([hashtable]$Config)
    
    # Decode salt and system entropy
    $salt = Decode-CustomBase64 -EncodedString $Config.Salt
    $systemEntropy = Decode-CustomBase64 -EncodedString $Config.SystemEntropy
    
    # Reconstruct key using distributed components
    $reconstructedKeyParts = @()
    $totalValidation = $true
    
    foreach ($split in $Config.KeySplits) {
        $decodedPart = Decode-CustomBase64 -EncodedString $split.Part
        $calculatedChecksum = (Get-FileHash -InputStream ([System.IO.MemoryStream]::new($decodedPart)) -Algorithm SHA256).Hash
        
        if ($calculatedChecksum -ne $split.Checksum) {
            Write-Error "Key integrity validation failed"
            return $null
        }
        
        $reconstructedKeyParts += $decodedPart
    }
    
    $reconstructedKey = [byte[]]$reconstructedKeyParts
    
    # Decrypt using reconstructed key
    $aes = [System.Security.Cryptography.AesManaged]::New()
    $aes.Key = $reconstructedKey
    $aes.IV = Decode-CustomBase64 -EncodedString $Config.EncryptedIV
    $aes.Mode = [System.Security.Cryptography.CipherMode]::CBC
    $aes.Padding = [System.Security.Cryptography.PaddingMode]::PKCS7
    
    $decryptor = $aes.CreateDecryptor()
    $encryptedBytes = Decode-CustomBase64 -EncodedString $Config.EncryptedScript
    $decryptedBytes = $decryptor.TransformFinalBlock($encryptedBytes, 0, $encryptedBytes.Length)
    
    return [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString($decryptedBytes)
}
